%% trade_lifecycle_sequence.mmd - Sequence diagram for end-to-end trade lifecycle
%% Actors: Client -> Broker -> RFQ Dealer -> Venue -> CCP -> Custodian -> DTCC -> CAT
%% Covers: RFQ -> RFE -> Order -> Execution -> Allocation -> Confirmation -> Clearing -> Settlement -> CAT submission

sequenceDiagram
 autonumber
 participant C as Client / Buy-side
 participant B as Broker / Sell-side
 participant D as RFQ Dealer
 participant V as Venue
 participant X as CCP
 participant U as Custodian
 participant T as DTCC / CSD
 participant R as FINRA CAT

 Note over C,B: Pre-trade
 C->>B: IOI posted
 C->>D: quote_request (MEQR)
 D-->>C: quote_event (MEQS) - bid/ask
 C->>D: quote_response (HIT/LIFT)
 C->>B: request_for_execution (RFE)

 Note over C,B: Order request (MEIR/MOIR)
 C->>B: order_request (cat_order_id)
 B->>R: MEIR event

 Note over B,V: Order open (MENO) and routing
 B->>V: order_event (MENO)
 B->>R: MENO event
 V-->>B: order acknowledged
 B->>V: order_route (MECO)
 B->>R: MECO event

 Note over V: Execution (MEOT)
 V-->>B: execution (MEOT) partial fill
 B->>R: MEOT event
 V-->>B: execution (MEOT) terminal fill
 B->>R: MEOT event

 Note over B,C: Allocation (MEPA / MEAA)
 B->>B: allocation split
 B->>R: MEPA event
 B-->>C: allocation_instruction
 C-->>B: affirm (CTM/DTCC-OASYS)
 B->>R: MEAA event

 Note over B,X: Clearing
 B->>X: trade for novation
 X-->>B: clearing_record accepted

 Note over B,U: Confirmation / Affirmation (Rule 15c6-2)
 B->>C: trade_confirmation sent
 C-->>B: affirmation_status = AFFIRMED

 Note over B,T: Settlement (T+1)
 B->>U: settlement_instruction
 U->>T: DVP settlement
 T-->>U: settlement_obligation = SETTLED
 U-->>B: settlement_status = SETTLED

 Note over R: T+1 08:00 - CAT deadline
 R-->>B: feedback file (errors/warnings)
 B->>R: MEOJ / MEOC corrections as needed (T+3)
